data.description: You DO NOT want to miss this awesome spacious home on a huge lot! Enjoy the newer roof, thermal windows, hot water heater, gutters, trim and garage doors. Bathrooms have newer tile floors, double vanity whirl pool and an oversized shower. Not only is the lot oversized, but the home also features 4 car garage space. 2 spaces are attached, 2 are detached next to the house. There is a 8X40 deck and a lot of room in the back perfect for entertaining or just letting the dogs run! Schedule your showing today! 2023-11-21
